4.Read contents of a file using for loop
In [16]:
f=open('example3.txt','r+')
lines=f.readlines()
for l in lines:
    print(l)
good morning to all

i am going to say wounderful topic 

to day
In [17]:
f.close()
5.Remove leading and traling spacesfrom a string
